en.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-V%C4%83n-Ho%C3%A8/Thu%E1%BB%B7-ti%C3%AAn-hoa/poem-6ZJvx8f9nvIiC2Ecf7S7GQ">Thuỷ tiên hoa - 水仙花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-V%C4%83n-Ho%C3%A8/author-eNwEHrle67jxtXPcXeJ4lg">Hoàng Văn Hoè</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C3%82m-d%E1%BA%A1-ph%C3%A1t/poem-WBlRALx57Yzq5dcby2KL7w">Tương Âm dạ phát - 湘陰夜發</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/V%E1%BB%8Dng-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng/poem-wJvMhctGGjp5x0fO5FyMJw">Vọng tưởng - 望想</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/author-5S8czaSOqXhHlNE7NtKr8g">Đặng Trần Côn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-H%C3%A0n/Y%C3%AAn-ca-h%C3%A0nh/poem-U9hCEqEHXob5E9lQKQQI9w">Yên ca hành - 燕歌行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-H%C3%A0n/author-DBXlWfBsak0HCC-xtJWBng">Đào Hàn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
